{"type": "article", "id": 30109, "title": "无线充电座", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-25T23:06:25Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 37, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160725222558slnBHEzuM6vqrFAQ.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>想让充电的过程变得更加优雅？在 Monowear Design 的设计师眼中，你需要的可能不仅仅是“无线化”：经过精心的设计，一个可以根据需要灵活调整并且同时为手机和 Apple Watch 充电的 MonoCharge 充电座诞生了。MonoCharge 采用模块化设计，两个具有无线充电功能的组件通过磁性相结合。它就好像是积木一样，只需要转换不同的贴合面，MonoCharge 就能在不三种不同的造型之间切换，携带起来非常方便，你也可以把它当作手机或者平板设备的支架使用。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1843570774/monocharge-wireless-charging-reimagined\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，早鸟价为 79 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160725224715QS6k4IzOlAwuWL3g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.882353\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160725224714gDcMvmwsp25jkCGZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.511765\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160725224715J0j7SeyiPosUK2gD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.670181\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160725224734SR7961sZQatDUNxV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}